    <item>
      <title>沙特上调 2 月份油价，因 OPEC+ 减产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/saudis-raise-february-crude-prices-as-opec-holds-back-barrels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯将于下个月提高针对亚洲买家的石油价格，这一迹象表明，在 OPEC+ 近期推迟了增产计划后，这个全球最大的原油出口国可能会在其最大的市场中看到供应收紧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/saudis-raise-february-crude-prices-as-opec-holds-back-barrels</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Jan 2025 06:08:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
